{"id":905106154,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"4Â months","timestamp":1677386774,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"6 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/905106154/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Edit Distance","memory":"42.5 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int minDistance(String s, String t) {\n        int m =s.length();\n        int n = t.length();\n        int[][] dp= new int[m+1][n+1];\n        for(int j=n-1;j>=0;j--){\n            dp[m][j]=n-j;\n        }\n        for(int j=m-1;j>=0;j--){\n            dp[j][n]=m-j;\n        }\n        \n        for(int i=m-1;i>=0;i--){\n            for(int j=n-1;j>=0;j--){\n                int ans;\n                if(s.charAt(i)==t.charAt(j)){\n                   ans=dp[i+1][j+1]; \n                }\n                else{\n                ans= Math.min(dp[i+1][j],Math.min(dp[i][j+1],dp[i+1][j+1]))+1;\n                }\n                dp[i][j]=ans;\n            }\n        }\n        return dp[0][0];\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"edit-distance","has_notes":false}
